&lt;h2 style="color:#0d1556;font-weight:bold;font-size:13pt;"&gt;
         TG4 Launch Irish Drama Adaptation Scheme
      &lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
         08 Oct 2009
      |
        
      &lt;br /&gt;
      &lt;br /&gt;
      
&lt;table style="padding-right:3px;" align="left" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"&gt;

&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;
              &lt;img src="http://www.iftn.ie/archive//storimag/tg4logo-f.gif" border="0" alt="" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#999999;font-size:xx-small;"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;

&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;div align="justify"&gt;&lt;b&gt;
    &lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;
TG4 has announced details of their latest development scheme, &amp;Uacute;dar,
which offers talented new Irish-language writers/directors the
opportunity to adapt a well-known original Irish language literary work
for television.&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;/b&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
          &lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;&amp;Uacute;dar aims to bring the selected work from a basic script stage to the broadcasting stage. 
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;This scheme, which is
co-sponsored by TG4 and Greas&amp;aacute;n na M&amp;eacute;an, is open to Irish language
writers from all over the country, whether they have screen experience
or not, and to directors who wish to gain experience in television
drama through Irish. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;To start the process
each applicant must choose an original piece of work in Irish, for
example a recognised short story. The applicant can arrange the work in
his or her own way by building on the story of the original work
(adhering to the time in which it is set) or by bringing it up-to-date.
The most important development, however, is to make the work suitable
for the television screen.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;The outline of the story
and 12 pages of sample script (= a number of scenes) must be enclosed
when sending the application form to TG4. Additional information is
available by ringing 091-558492 or by emailing &lt;a href="mailto:christine@greasannamean.ie?SUBJECT=From%20the%20IFTN%20Site"&gt;christine@greasannamean.ie&lt;/a&gt; 
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;Applicants will be
competing in a script competition. From this competition nine will be
selected to attend craft master-classes conducted by a script editor
where each proposal will be developed further. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;Six drama scripts will
be chosen for television production from the nine proposed scripts.
These will be developed through the directing workshop before being
produced and broadcast on TG4 in 2010.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;Application forms and details of the scheme are available at &lt;a target="new" href="http://www.tg4.ie/"&gt;www.tg4.ie&lt;/a&gt; 
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;Applicants must send application forms, the outline and the sample script to:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;Com&amp;oacute;rtas &amp;Uacute;dar&lt;br /&gt;
f/c Greas&amp;aacute;n na M&amp;eacute;an, &lt;br /&gt;
An Chuasn&amp;oacute;g, &lt;br /&gt;
Baile Ard, &lt;br /&gt;
An Spid&amp;eacute;al, &lt;br /&gt;
Co. na Gaillimhe&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;Deadline midday 16 November 2009.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&amp;Uacute;dar &amp;ndash; Com&amp;oacute;rtas do dhr&amp;aacute;ma&amp;iacute;ocht teilif&amp;iacute;se&lt;/b&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;Sc&amp;eacute;im fhorbartha &amp;iacute; seo a
thugann deis do thallann nua scr&amp;iacute;bhneoir&amp;iacute;/sti&amp;uacute;rth&amp;oacute;ir&amp;iacute; le Gaeilge,
saothar aitheanta a athch&amp;oacute;iri&amp;uacute; don teilif&amp;iacute;se agus a thabhairt &amp;oacute; ch&amp;eacute;im
bhunscripte chuig c&amp;eacute;im chraolta. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;T&amp;aacute; an sc&amp;eacute;im seo, at&amp;aacute;
comhurraithe ag TG4 agus Gr&amp;eacute;as&amp;aacute;n na Me&amp;aacute;n, oscailte do scr&amp;iacute;bhneoir&amp;iacute;
Gaeilge &amp;oacute; cheann ceann na t&amp;iacute;re, b&amp;iacute;odh taith&amp;iacute; sc&amp;aacute;ile&amp;aacute;in acu n&amp;oacute; n&amp;aacute; b&amp;iacute;odh,
agus do sti&amp;uacute;rth&amp;oacute;ir&amp;iacute; ar mhian leo taith&amp;iacute; a fh&amp;aacute;il ar dhr&amp;aacute;ma&amp;iacute;ocht
teilif&amp;iacute;se i nGaeilge. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;Mar th&amp;uacute;s leis an
bpr&amp;oacute;iseas, roghn&amp;oacute;idh gach iarrth&amp;oacute;ir bunshaothar Gaeilge, mar shampla
gearrsc&amp;eacute;al aitheanta. Tig leis an iarrth&amp;oacute;ir a ch&amp;oacute;iri&amp;uacute; f&amp;eacute;in a chur air
tr&amp;iacute; th&amp;oacute;g&amp;aacute;il ar chreatlach an bhunshaothair (clo&amp;iacute; leis an saol ina
bhfuil s&amp;eacute; lonnaithe) n&amp;oacute; &amp;eacute; a thabhairt suas chun d&amp;aacute;ta. Is &amp;iacute; an fhorbairt
is t&amp;aacute;bhachta&amp;iacute;, &amp;aacute;fach, n&amp;aacute; an saothar a chur in oiri&amp;uacute;int don sc&amp;aacute;ile&amp;aacute;in
teilif&amp;iacute;se.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;N&amp;iacute; m&amp;oacute;r Iml&amp;iacute;ne den sc&amp;eacute;al
chomh maith le 12 leathanach de script samplach (= roinnt radharcanna)
agus an fhoirm iarratais faoi iamh a sheoladh chugainn. Is f&amp;eacute;idir breis
eolas a lorg ach glaoch ar 091-558492 n&amp;oacute; r-phost a sheoladh chuig &lt;a href="mailto:christine@greasannamean.ie?SUBJECT=From%20the%20IFTN%20Site"&gt;christine@greasannamean.ie&lt;/a&gt; 

&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;Beidh na hiarrth&amp;oacute;ir&amp;iacute; san
ioma&amp;iacute;ocht i gcom&amp;oacute;rtas scripte. &amp;Oacute;n gcom&amp;oacute;rtas seo roghn&amp;oacute;far naon&amp;uacute;r le
freastal ar mh&amp;aacute;istir&amp;ndash;ranganna ceirde, faoi sti&amp;uacute;ir eagarth&amp;oacute;ir scripte,
ag a nd&amp;eacute;anfar forbairt bhreise ar gach togra. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;As an 9 togra scripte
roghn&amp;oacute;far 6 dr&amp;aacute;ma le l&amp;eacute;iri&amp;uacute; do theilif&amp;iacute;s. D&amp;eacute;anfar forbairt orthu sin ag
ceardlann sti&amp;uacute;rth&amp;oacute;ireachta sula nd&amp;eacute;anfar iad a l&amp;eacute;iri&amp;uacute; agus a chraoladh
ar TG4 in 2010.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;T&amp;aacute; foirm iarratais agus sonra&amp;iacute; na sc&amp;eacute;ime le f&amp;aacute;il ar &lt;a target="new" href="http://www.tg4.ie/"&gt;www.tg4.ie&lt;/a&gt; 
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;N&amp;iacute; fol&amp;aacute;ir d&amp;rsquo;iarrth&amp;oacute;ir&amp;iacute; foirm iarratais, iml&amp;iacute;ne agus script samplach a sheoladh sa phost chuig:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;Com&amp;oacute;rtas  &amp;Uacute;dar &lt;br /&gt;
Gr&amp;eacute;as&amp;aacute;n na Me&amp;aacute;n &lt;br /&gt;
Eo Teilif&amp;iacute;s &lt;br /&gt;
An Spid&amp;eacute;al &lt;br /&gt;
Co. na Gaillimhe &lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color:#0d1556;font-size:x-small;"&gt;le go mbeidh s&amp;iacute; faighte againn roimh mhe&amp;aacute;nlae 16 Samhain 2009.&lt;/span&gt;
          &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="clear:both;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>